      "role": "user",
      "content": "small reasons? i don't see any. there's nothing left to read or breathe for. it's like i'm just performing these little tasks for a life that ended months ago. everything feels so pointless. honestly, it feels like there's no point in even fighting to stay here when the person who made being \"here\" worth it is just... gone. it's just exhausting.",
