      "role": "user",
      "content": "rest doesn't really help. it doesn't change the fact that i'm just alone. it feels more like i'm just being cruel to myself by forcing myself to keep going when the connection is severed. like, if the most important part of my life is gone, isn't the rest of it just... unnecessary? it's so hard to see the logic in struggling through this just to be miserable.",
